The BMFH_Template type exposes the following members.

Methods

  NameDescription
BMFH_CreateBiometricHeaderTemplate
Factory constructor for generating biometric header templates.
BMFH_CreateExtendedBiometricHeaderTemplate
Factory constructor for generating biometric header templates with the added finger parameter which should be used to maintain tracking from a tagged image.
BMFH_GetBiometricHeaderWithFinger
A special routine for returning the extended finger tagged biometric header field of the template.

Fields

  NameDescription
LONG_HEADER_LENGTH
The length of a finger identifier extended biometric header.
SHORT_HEADER_LENGTH
The length of a standard biometric header.

The validation data if present.
